{{Top|leg}}
A '''boarding harpoon''' was a [[flexiglass]] weapon with a superheated tip used for boarding enemy [[Starship/Legends|vessels]]. The harpoon was filled with [[coma gas]] and fired at the other ship. During flight, the weapon's [[Armor/Legends|armored]] tip was superheated and would puncture the target's [[Hull/Legends|hull]]. Once the harpoon penetrated the ship, the tip would fuse with the hull, making removal impossible; in addition the gas was released, rendering anyone who came in contact with it unconscious. This weapon, usually illegal, was used by the [[Myrkr strike team]] to incapacitate the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] warriors on the ship they subsequently commandeered for transport to [[Myrkr/Legends|Myrkr]].

